extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Back To Lookout
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Retour au Point de Vue

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Lea, chérie!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Lea, chérie !

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: I guess we're pretty much in sync with the dungeon.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: J'imagine qu'on est assez synchronisé avec le donjon.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: You just fought one of these statue guardians too, right?
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Tu viens juste de combattre une de ces statues gardiennes, pas vrai ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: [nods]
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: [acquiesce]

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: I like those enemies!\. They're fun to fight!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: J'aime bien ces ennemis !\. Ils sont marrants à combattre !

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: They're formidable opponents to be sure.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Ce sont des adversaires redoutables, ça c'est certain.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Oui! It's a great feeling to get close for a beating right after dodging their shield!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Oui ! C'est tellement réjouissant de se rapprocher pour les battre juste après avoir évité leur bouclier !

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: But I guess things would be different for a Hexacast, right?
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Mais j'imagine que les choses doivent être différentes pour un Hexacast, non ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: More ranged attacks and the like.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Plus d'attaques à distance et tout.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Not necessarily.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Pas nécessairement.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: We have a number of close-combat moves at our disposal as well.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: On a aussi tout une série de mouvements de combat rapproché à notre disposition.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: And I happen to prefer those as well.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Et il se trouve que je les préfères.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Ah, a man of culture!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Ah, un homme de culture !

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Let's go then! Off to punching more statues!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Allons-y alors ! Allons cogner plus de statues !
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.note: could be weird out of context

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Indeed.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Allons-y.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Hey!\. Those signs just appeared!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Hé !\. Ces signes viennent d'apparaître !

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Yes and those depictions are quite interesting as well!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Oui, et ces représentations sont aussi très intéressantes !

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Do you think there's an elevator inside?
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Est-ce que tu penses qu'il y a un ascenseur à l'intérieur ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Possibly!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Possiblement !

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: I guess the Ancients pretty much learned the elevator technology ever since the Temple Mine.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: J'imagine que les anciens ont découvert la technologie des ascenseurs depuis le Temple de la Mine.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: No, Buggy. If there is an elevator, it won't be based on human technology.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Non, Buggy. S'il y a un ascenseur, il sera pas basé sur de la technologie humaine.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: You see, this temple must be much older than the Temple Mine.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Tu vois, ce temple doit être bien plus ancien que le Temple de la Mine.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: It's a place mentioned in the old texts of the Ancients.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: C'est un endroit mentionné dans les textes des Anciens.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: So it must have been here long before humankind arrived.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Donc il devait avoir été là bien avant que l'humanité arrive.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Oh yeah, that makes sense!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Oh oui, ça serait logique !

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Still, I bet it's an elevator!\. Let's see what's inside!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Mais bon, je parie que c'est un ascenseur !\. Voyons voir ce qu'il y a à l'intérieur !

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Hey! The view from here is awesome isn't it?
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Hé ! La vue d'ici est vraiment grandiose, pas vrai ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: [nods]
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: [acquiesce]

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Did you see the crystals at the top?
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Tu as vu les cristaux en haut ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Those huge crystals that stretch over the whole crater.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Ces cristaux géants qui s'étendent sur tout le cratère.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Some people think they're connected to some Ancient magic to cover up the whole place.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Certaines personnes pensent qu'ils sont liés à de la magie des Anciens pour recouvrir tout l'endroit.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: That's probably why it remained hidden up until now.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: C'est probablement pour ça qu'il est resté caché jusqu'à maintenant.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: I told you!\. They did it again!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Je te l'avais dit !\. Ils ont remis ça !

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Hey, at least it's not a giant tree that leads up to space!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Hé, au moins c'est pas un arbre géant qui monte dans l'espace !

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: It's still bad!\. A crater!\. A very, very deep crater!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: C'est nul quand même ! C'est un cratère !\. Un cratère vraiment, vraiment très profond !

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: You know... I thought at this point you'd be able to handle this.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Tu sais... je pensais que depuis le temps, tu pourrais supporter ça.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: We haven't been playing CrossWorlds for a long time, right?
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: On a plus trop joué à CrossWorlds ces derniers temps, non ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: I entirely forgot how bad this game was with heights.
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: J'ai complètement oublié à quel point ce jeu était nul sur les hauteurs.

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Wow, that's deep!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Ouah, c'est profond !

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: You can barely see anything because of the fog...
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: On voit à peine quelque chose à cause du brouillard...

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: That makes it even more mysterious!
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Ça rend ça encore plus mystérieux !

extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.orig: Teleport Back
extension/post-game/data/maps/final-dng/.text: Se Téléporter de Retour
